   <head>To the Gentle Reader.</head>
   <p>Being very loathe (Gentle Reader) to varrie, of wilful<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>nes,
or securitie, from the trueth of our written copie: we
haue thought it necessarie, to make this compendious &amp; ex<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>act
retractation of errours escaped in this impression.</p>
